    <item>
      <title>Le Pen的法国总统竞标被上诉法院保持活力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/french-appeals-court-expects-to-rule-on-le-pen-case-by-mid-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴黎上诉法院表示应该能够在明年夏天之前对她的定罪和选举禁令作出裁决后，海洋勒庞的希望保持其2027年法国总统竞标的希望得到了推动。比预期要早得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/french-appeals-court-expects-to-rule-on-le-pen-case-by-mid-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
